{"title":"外国谚语（美洲）","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"外国谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（美洲）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魔鬼总是相似的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对待狼只能用棍棒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煽风者必陷于风暴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谬误从门缝钻进，真理立于门前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹日晒的脸，不怕阳光灼热。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有经验的渔民，总能对付风暴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥远的路途，从近处始步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懂得自己无知，说明已有所获。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍柴方知斧钝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正义的人朋友多。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}